snippet.title: Varney Lake: Release Date Teaser
snippet.description:
Wishlist: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1933180/Varney_Lake/

Summer, 1954. A perfect vacation awaits three best friends, playing games, making crazy plans, and running from bullies... Until they meet the vampire.
Find out what really happened that Summer at Varney Lake when it launches April 28th 2023.
